{"tid":259921,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「我廠必勝」天天天，你地聲震天😎","createTime":"2017-05-27T10:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T13:55:43.000Z","uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62bd07f7a782c15a2c0bf73c33a65782fbcb4be2","tid":259921,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:25:19.000Z","msg":"比你地今年拎到歐聯入場券又如何，咪俾你地戀棧多一年歐聯出局嘅歷史。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n何必笑我地雲爺爺呢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講番今年聯賽，俾啲掌聲先啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中學陸運會指定動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天天天，你地聲震天。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地地地，雖然你地有歐聯贏我地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地聲震天，你地聯賽排名又贏左我地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我地實攞足總冠軍，我廠冠軍必袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑我地，又如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1828a1878d90c2a0819ad1ac18fb87bd109cd3e","tid":259921,"uid":10313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4e90525a5d89b5dc886bf543b4c20532a41ba3","tid":259921,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:26:52.000Z","msg":"創意台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4b07824ef128ff4597430c17ef4953af6d3519","tid":259921,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>創意台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac